data.name: Label6.Text
data.value: We are committed to helping you take control of your financial future, with the tools to track your expenses effortlessly, helping you save more, spend wisely, and achieve your financial goals. M.E.T empower individuals to take control of their financial future withan intuitive, easy-to-use platform that enables them to track spending, set goals, and stay within budget.

data.name: Label16.Text
data.value: At M.E.T, we understand the challenges of managing your finances in today's fast-paced world. With increasing expenses and the growing need for financial planning, it’s easy to lose track of where your money is going. Our team of financial experts and tech enthusiasts developed M.E.T to make budgeting simple, accessible, and efficient.
